  <title>Pin-Joint</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Definition<keyword>Hinge Joint</keyword><keyword>Pin-Joint</keyword><keyword>Pivot Point</keyword><keyword>Revolute Joint</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="2" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:158px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="PinJointSymbols2.bmp" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Pin-Joint</text> forces <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Sketch-Element-Point" styleclass="Element">Points</link> from two separate <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">parts</text> to be coincident.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The two <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Parts</text> rotate relative to each other, with the <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Pin-Joint</text> their center-of-rotation.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">There are two <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Symbols">Symbols</link> for a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Pin-Joint</text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;">:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:6pt; vertical-align:sub;"></image> a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Circle</text>, slightly larger than a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Point</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Normal">&#32;</text>a &apos;Dowel&apos; Symbol when fixed to the <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Base-Part.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Pin-Joint</text> is also known as a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Revolute Joint</text>, or a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Hinge Joint</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dyad">Dyads</link></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">See</text><text style="font-weight:normal;">:</text>&#32;<link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Slide-Joint">Slide-Joint</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Ball-Joints">Ball-Joint</link></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-weight:normal;">See also:</text>&#32;<link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Mechanism-Pin-Joint">Add Pin-Joint</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Mechanism-Slide-Joint">Add Slide-Joint</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Mechanism-Ball-Joint">Add Ball-Joint</link>. </para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
